Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From a different perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An imposing wall is just a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stuntmen are so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Behind the flashy scenes, we catch a glimpse of a tragic case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamen Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shall not get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I'd let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:46.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,THE CAR STUNT'S UTMOST LIMIT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't execute a plan like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's way too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:59.69,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Fukamachi Shinji (30)\NDirector
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:59.69,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nakasato Hidehiko (28)\NAssistant Director
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think so as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell was talking to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep your mouth shut, newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's definitely dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:07.99,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Rikiishi Kengo (38)\NStuntman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For any other stuntman but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can nail this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've lost count of how many of these I've done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Kijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:14.46,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kijima Daisaku (40)\NCameraman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's run through it without stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget the trick photography.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the time I drive up the ramp until the car falls, one cut is all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if I'm filming from below, the camera won't record you jumping out of the car to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just not the stuntman that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot for letting us come today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But having the chance to see a Kamen Yaiba show filming is so awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's our Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sure is well-shown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you're looking for, "well-known."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at all these Kamen Yaiba stickers they gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've almost got the whole set.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think I've lost my touch, just say it to my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sure sound angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with the technology we have now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're able to increase the intensity and quality of the shot much better than with only an actual stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't think old-school stunts are necessary anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car the monster drives reaches the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He parks the first car, now called Car A.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The camera switches to the remote-controlled Car B.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In place of Car A the monster was driving, Car B turns and speeds ahead toward the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, the edited shot with the explosion doesn't show the car falling to the pavement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, once we add some digital enhancements...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stunt for that scene will be more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.22,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nishiwaki Masao (45)\NMechanical Technician
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Steering wheel, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brake, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and decide already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How the mighty have fallen, Kijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking orders from a kid like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the plan we've decided on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already got the producers' permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're gonna regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scenes where Kamen Yaiba appears are so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, with the swooshes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the part with all the flashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once we finish our meals, we'll be doing the next take.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're now on standby, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He kinda has an attitude problem, that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter, he's gonna get beaten by Yaiba anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just what he gets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what happening during the show, not real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is kinda boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came all this way, and they're not even filming anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's their lunch break so there's no helping that, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, how about we have our lunch now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did everyone receive a lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My stomach's growling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your stomach reacts quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Kamen Yaiba\NTo Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure my signature's good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, they have the same license plate number and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once on the roof, these two cars will switch places...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the remote-controlled one will be driven over the side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, here's a little souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop that, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're still meddling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not meddling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two are arguing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to say that... Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope they can start filming without too many problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it won't be so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did it start already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He plans to do his version of the stunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you it was too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seatbelt's a bit loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the roof, he was on the verge of unfastening the belt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But didn't get out of the car in time and got caught in the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Cameraman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were filming just a minute ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you play it back for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Better check up there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's working ahead of us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what are you doing, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a very carefully planned murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased was a stuntman named Rikiishi Kengo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 38.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the cause of death found to be from the fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the car crashed into the ground, the impact from the collision ran through his entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having a person in a car that's dropped from such a high place...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's quite a dangerous way to film something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd never be allowed to do a stunt like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s the one who decided to do the stunt like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It backfired on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be more precise, it wasn't a stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a performance before the real shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was feeling the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Feeling the pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can understand how he felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Younger guys just keep getting hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if I ever asked to do anything else other than film, they'd fire me as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that we don't need stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're especially important for this kind of story?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with the digital technology we have now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're able to create some great scenes without using old-school methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truth is, there are plenty who think using CG alone is more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what can I do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The producers are the ones with the final say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that the producers planned to fire Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, but you convinced them not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're gonna regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, no matter how you look at it, he was in a rush to keep the job he was barely holding onto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must have been it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe what I'm hearing, Kijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one who talked to the producers and made it hard for him to keep his job in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how he did it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} somehow knew all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that why you think I had it in for that bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once he found out about your crappy maintenance habits, you're the one he ended up punching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't the place to be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, you got slapped around by that bastard quite a few times, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you yelled, "I'll kill him" at more than one of the drinking parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, are you saying I did something more than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, please just set the record straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was an accident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To see if there was some failure in the car itself, well have the maintenance staff thoroughly check over the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way that was the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mechanics were flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you still have a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But under the circumstances, it's probable that it was ultimately an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Uh... That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was a murder crafted to appear like an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, calm yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to confirm about the deceased Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For instance, whether or not he'd want to perform a stunt even more because of the risk involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was someone who rushed to try something a little more dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always had been.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was always "survival of the fittest" for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, when someone does a stunt like that, they have to go through intense training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the guys who can do the stunt are ultimately the best ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially when he was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lately, he'd probably been afraid of losing that title.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if the murderer latched on to that weakness of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you explain further?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fukamachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:16:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you talking about with Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} before he jumped in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told me, "I'll show you what a real stunt looks like."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he ignored my protests and leapt into the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got it backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meaning that it wasn't Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, but you, Fukamachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe by saying something like, "We might be on different sides, but depending on your performance..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You might convince everyone to change their minds."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all you'd need to say to prompt him into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, are you trying to say that I killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the murderer, Fukamachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if Fukamachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did provoke him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the one who drove the car and misjudged the actual stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way that can count as murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Fukamachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said this to take advantage of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"There's no air bomb in the back of Car A."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It's pointless to perform the stunt using only Car A."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Don't even think about it"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phrasing it like that only made Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} more determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once he reached the roof, he quickly changed to Car B where the explosive was installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, on the verge of dropping off the roof, he'd perform the most dangerous part of the stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He thought, "I'll show them how good I am."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means that the car that fell from the roof is Car B?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one doesn't have an explosive inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Car A!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I'm all confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case, go check the car on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has to be Car B.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't switch from Car A to Car B.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He performed the stunt in the original car, made a mistake, and fell over the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like we thought, an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, don't be so quick to decide on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember how Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} looked immediately following the crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we could see the photos the forensics investigator took of the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is, right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Yaiba sticker that Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} put on the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stuck it on the car the vehicle specialist guy drove up to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have changed cars on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I put stickers on both cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that we can't prove whether or not he switched cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is what you're meant to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you show me the video again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:18:59.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His cape isn't caught in the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't appear as if he opened or closed the door of the vehicle on the way up the ramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what about the explosive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the culprit had to do is stash it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that alone isn't enough to prove that he switched cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went up to the roof right after the accident, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found that the hood of the car was hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if the car had just been shut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that indicates...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example, just for example, if I'd convinced him to do it, and he switched cars on the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he didn't get clear of the car before it fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be cruel, but it's his own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean he "lost his touch"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of trying to tear off his seatbelt, he should have put on the emergency brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was impossible for him to use the brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of vehicle Car B was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something in addition to being the base for the air explosive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was remote-controlled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where is that remote control now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that he wanted to check on it, so I lent it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we use this, we'll definitely find out which car was which, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinda sounds like it's crying, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:20:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I used the production money to pay it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anyone found out, I'd be fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why you used Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s weakness against him and contrived a plan to murder him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} reached the roof in Car A, you waited until he changed vehicles...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then operated the remote control, directing its every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the brake wouldn't work and the door wouldn't open, you made him fall over the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And afterwards, Rikiishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s death would be deemed an accident he caused himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as everyone thought that he died in Car A...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could return the remote to the vehicle specialist Nishiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with everyone being none the wiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't eat another bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yaiba's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.45,0:23:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no good, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put as many stickers on me as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm beyond repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got that right.
